title: FizzBuzz
description:
Write a function `fizz_buzz` that takes an integer `n` and prints the numbers from 1 to n (inclusive), but for multiples of three print "Fizz" instead of the number and for multiples of five print "Buzz". For numbers which are multiples of both three and five print "FizzBuzz".

#### Function Signature
``python
def fizz_buzz(n: int):
```
